{{Vgname|危机之前 -最终幻想VII-|ja=ビフォア クライシス -ファイナルファンタジーVII-|en=Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII}}是一款由[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯]]开发并发售的[[移动电话|移动电话]]平台[[游戏软件|游戏软件]]。2004年9月24日首次发布，最早的对应机种仅为[[NTT_DOCOMO|NTTDoCoMo]]的[[I-mode|I-mode]]终端[[FOMA|FOMA]]900i之后机型，之后[[ソフトバンクモバイル|SoftBank Mobile]]旗下的{{tsl|ja|Yahoo!ケータイ||雅虎手机}}以及[[Au_(行動電話)|au]]旗下的{{tsl|ja|EZweb}}也分别于2007年1月30日和2007年4月5日开始被提供支持<ref name=spot>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/mobile/rpg/beforecrisisfinalfantasyvii/tech_info.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;techinfo|title=Before Crisis Tech Info|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2008-04-09}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。本作为“[[最终幻想VII补完计划|最终幻想VII补完计划]]”系列作品之一。

本文以下简称为《危机之前》。

==游戏可玩性==
[[File:Before_Crisis_gameplay.jpg|thumb]]

《危机之前》是一款{{tsl|en|Time-keeping systems in games#Real-time||实时}}动作角色扮演游戏。游戏采用[[二维计算机图形|2D]][[橫向捲軸遊戲|橫向捲軸]]推进的方式令玩家操纵人物移动。在[[可玩性|游戏可玩性]]方面，游戏提供有多种模式的玩法。“情节模式”是玩家通过游玩游戏的主要故事情节，完成各项任务，来继续进行游戏。“自由模式”则允许玩家漫步于城镇中同乡民们对话<ref name=IGN-handson>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/09/01/hands-on-before-crisis-final-fantasy-vii|title=Hands On: Before Crisis Final Fantasy VII|accessdate=2013-04-04|date=2004-08-31|author=Anoop Gantayat|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021003826/https://www.ign.com/articles/2004/09/01/hands-on-before-crisis-final-fantasy-vii|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家也可以游玩额外的任务来获得[[经验值|经验值]]（XP）和物品，其中有些是“自由模式”独有的。

游戏中的角色都有[[生命值|生命值]]（HP）和[[魔法值|魔法值]]（MP），而且在获得一定的经验值之后可以[[Experience_point#Level-based_progression|升级]]至特定的值点以装备新的武器和盔甲。玩家可以通过手机的十字键来操控游戏人物，右功能键可以用来施放魔法<ref name="IGN-handson" />。在战斗中玩家可以选择手动攻击的敌人或按下操作键自动攻击最近的敌人<ref name=E3-handson>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/05/09/e3-2006-before-crisis-hands-on|title=E3 2006: Before Crisis Hands-On|accessdate=2013-04-04|date=2006-05-09|author=Levi Buchanan|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502115535/https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/05/09/e3-2006-before-crisis-hands-on|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==开发==
本作是史克威尔艾尼克斯首个专门为[[移动电话|手机]]平台开发的原创游戏，其以包月{{tsl|en|subscription business model||订购}}的形式发布在[[NTT_DoCoMo|NTT DoCoMo]]旗下[[Freedom_of_Mobile_Multimedia_Access|FOMA]]品牌iMode产品线下<!--It was the first original game to be produced by Square Enix exclusively for [[mobile_phone|mobile phone]]s, and was released on [[NTT_DoCoMo|NTT DoCoMo]]'s [[Freedom_of_Mobile_Multimedia_Access|FOMA]] iMode line of phones on a monthly  [[subscription_business_model|subscription]] basis.--><ref name=fivejapanese/>。本作也是“[[最终幻想VII补完计划|最终幻想VII补完计划]]”系列中第二个被公布的作品，但却在《[[最终幻想VII_降临之子|最终幻想VII 降临之子]]》因[[后期制作|后期制作]]而推迟上映时率先发售<!--It was the second title announced in the ''[[Compilation_of_Final_Fantasy_VII|Compilation of Final Fantasy VII]]'' series, although it was the first to be released, after the film ''[[Final_Fantasy_VII:_Advent_Children|Final Fantasy VII: Advent Children]]'' was delayed in [[post-production|post-production]].--><ref name="acunveiledandscreened">{{Cite book | year=2006 | editor=Watanabe, Yukari | title=Final Fantasy VII Advent Children – Reunion Files – | url=https://archive.org/details/finalfantasyviia00libg | language=ja | publisher=SoftBank | isbn=4-7973-3498-3 | page=[https://archive.org/details/finalfantasyviia00libg/page/n75 74]}}</ref><ref name="acunveiled2">{{cite web | author=IGNPS2 | year=2003 | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/451/451541p1.html | title=TGS 2003: Final Fantasy VII: The Movie? | work=IGN | accessdate=August 11, 2006 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060822080601/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/451/451541p1.html | archivedate=2006年8月22日 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在2005年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展前新闻发布会上，史克威尔艾尼克斯宣布游戏的英文版本将于2006年在美国发布<!--In their pre-[[Electronic_Entertainment_Expo|E3]], 2005 press conference, Square Enix announced that an English version of the game would be released in the United States in 2006, although no such game was ever released.--><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/2005/05/16/news_6124974.html |title=Final Fantasy VII: Before Crisis bound for US mobiles - News at GameSpot |publisher=Square Enix |first=Steve |last=Palley |work=GameSpot |date=May 16, 2005 |accessdate=2008-10-13 |archive-date=2009-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307035558/http://www.gamespot.com/news/2005/05/16/news_6124974.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年[[东京电玩展|东京电玩展]]结束后，游戏额外新增两家日本移动运营商，分别是2007年1月开始支持运作的[[軟銀集團|SoftBank Mobile]]，以及2007年4月支持运作的[[Au_(行動電話)|EZweb]]<!--Following an announcement at the [[Tokyo_Game_Show|Tokyo Game Show]] in 2006, the game was released for two additional Japanese mobile carriers, [[SoftBank_Mobile|SoftBank Mobile]], in January 2007, and [[au_(mobile_phone_company)|EZweb]], in April 2007. --><ref name="EZweb-release">{{Cite web | title=『ビフォアクライシス-FFVII-』がついにEZwebでも配信開始に！ | url=http://www.famitsu.com/k_tai/news/2007/04/05/607,1175766013,69697,0,0.html | language=ja | publisher=Famitsu | date=2007-04-05 | accessdate=2013-04-23 | archive-date=2007-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070706081706/http://www.famitsu.com/k_tai/news/2007/04/05/607,1175766013,69697,0,0.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年，史克威尔艾尼克斯的制作人田畑端曾在推特上发表其想将危机之前移植至[[Nintendo_3DS|Nintendo 3DS]]的愿望，“重新进行方案的结构和游戏设计”，支持大量的塔克斯成员玩家同时进行游戏使其更像是一款[[動作角色扮演遊戲|动作RPG]]<!--In 2010 Square Enix producer Hajime Tabata tweeted his desire to remake Before Crisis for the [[Nintendo_3DS|Nintendo 3DS]] and "redo the scenario structure and game design" to make it more like an [[action_RPG|action RPG]] where "a large number of Turks players play simultaneously."--><ref name="3DS">{{Cite web | date=September 30, 2010 | author=Pigna, Kris | url=http://www.1up.com/news/mulls-before-crisis-3ds-remake | title=Square Enix Producer Mulls Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII 3DS Remake | work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | accessdate=31 March 2013 | archive-date=2015-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005103703/http://www.1up.com/news/mulls-before-crisis-3ds-remake | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[野村哲也|野村哲也]]和[[Yoshinori_Kitase|北濑佳范]]对此也表示很感兴趣<!--[[Tetsuya_Nomura|Tetsuya Nomura]] and [[Yoshinori_Kitase|Yoshinori Kitase]] were also interested.--><ref name="3DS"/>。当被问及游戏的[[本地化|本地化]]情况时，藤田敬二（Keiji Fujita）在发布将登陆美国市场的消息之后没有新进展<!--When asked about the game's localization, Keiji Fujita admitted that after the game was announced for US, no progress. -->。他进一步解释说，由于游戏是属于在线游戏，当时美国市场的功能手机普遍规格较低而不适于游戏的本地化，本作仅适用于在日本市场的高端手机。<!--He further explains that feature phones were to low spect to localize to the US at the time and because it is an online game, it was only available for high end phones in Japan. -->藤田同时指出游戏没有被移植的另一个可能原因是由于游戏制作人离职并投入游戏厂商[[Capcom|Capcom]]的缘故<!--Fujita noted possible reasons for the game not being ported was due to the games producer leaving for game maker [[Capcom|Capcom]].--><ref name="explanation">{{Cite web | date=April 4, 2010 | author=Spencer | url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/04/04/after-square-enix-announced-it-what-ever-happened-to-before-crisis-final-fantasy-vii/ | title=After Square Enix Announced It, What Ever Happened To Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII? | work=Siliconera | accessdate=4 April 2013 | archive-date=2014-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019172447/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/04/04/after-square-enix-announced-it-what-ever-happened-to-before-crisis-final-fantasy-vii/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
《危机之前》普遍获得了评论家们的积极反映。AnimeFringe评价游戏的特效看起来“相当的好”，并对游戏通过使塔克斯（Turks）成员作为主角而雪崩（AVALANCHE）则为反派角色来“扭转好人与坏人角色”表示称赞<ref name="fringe">{{cite web |url=http://www.animefringe.com/magazine/2005/12/feature/01-4.php |date= |title=The Legacy of Final Fantasy VII |first=Janet |last=Crocker |first2=Lesley |last2=Smith |first3=Tim |last3=Henderson |first4=Adam |last4=Arnold |publisher=AnimeFringe |accessdate=August 17, 2010 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BcojXstw?url=http://www.animefringe.com/magazine/2005/12/feature/01-4.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。RPGamer的Cara Lee Haslam在[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展会上试玩过游戏之后指出，“游戏的绘图方面真棒，尤其是对于一个手机游戏来说，”尽管如此，她也指出游戏在动画方面“还不是最好的。”<ref name="rpg">{{cite web | url=http://www.rpgamer.com/event/e3-2006/impressions/ff7bc01.html | date=May 12, 2006 | title=E3 Impression Final Fantasy VII: Before Crisis | first=Cara Lee | last=Haslam | publisher=RPGamer | accessdate=August 17, 2010 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68Zt8PkPq?url=http://www.rpgamer.com/event/e3-2006/impressions/ff7bc01.html | archivedate=2012年6月21日 }}</ref>[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的Bethany Massimilla也在E3展会上试玩了游戏，并对其大加称赞<ref name="spotty">{{cite web |url=http://uk.gamespot.com/mobile/rpg/beforecrisisfinalfantasyvii/news.html?sid=6150317&mode=previews |date=May 10, 2006 |title=E3 06: Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII Hands-On Impressions |first=Bethany |last=Masimilla |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=August 17, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68Zt9SGay?url=http://uk.gamespot.com/before-crisis-final-fantasy-vii/previews/e3-06-before-crisis-final-fantasy-vii-hands-on-impressions-6150317/ |archivedate=2012年6月21日 }}</ref>。游戏投放市场的当天吸引了20万用户上线注册，成为当时在[[手机游戏|手机平台]]上[[最畅销电子游戏列表#移动电话|销量最高的游戏]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Winkler|first=Chris|title=Before Crisis: Final Fantasy VII Registers 200,000 Users on Day One|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2004/1812.html|publisher=RPGFan|accessdate=21 July 2012|date=2004-09-14|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906015739/http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2004/1812.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]将本作列为五大最不可能登陆北美市场的日本经典游戏之一<ref name=fivejapanese>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/features/japanese-cell-phone-treasures|title=Japanese Cell Phone Treasures: 5 Mobile Games We Won't Be Seeing|accessdate=2013-03-31|date=2012-09-20|author=Chris Pereira|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|language=|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808114627/http://www.1up.com/features/japanese-cell-phone-treasures|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

